<TEXT>
<P>
ATHENS, December 8 (Xinhua) -- Federico Mayor, director general
of the United Nations Educational, Scientific and Cultural
Organization (UNESCO), said today that balance must be kept
between development and environmental protection.
</P>
<P>
Addressing a five-day conference of the "Environment and
Society: Education and Public awareness" which opened today in the
northern Greek port city of Thessaloniki, Mayor said that the time
