<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, December 9 (Xinhua) -- The Second China Shipowners
Association (CSA) Conference opened today in Beijing, with CSA
Chairman Chen Zhongbiao calling on all members to unite in order
to meet growing challenges in the international shipping market.
</P>
<P>
Vice-Minister of Communications Liu Songjin, who also serves as
honorary chairman of the CSA, noted that the organization was
founded in 1993 and currently has 177 members.
</P>
