<HEADLINE> Vietnam, U.S. Sign Health Cooperation Agreement </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
HANOI, December 9 (Xinhua) -- Vietnam and the United States
signed an agreement of cooperation on health care and health
research here monday, local press reported today.
