<HEADLINE> Russia, Ukraine Set up Cooperation Group </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
MOSCOW, December 8 (Xinhua) -- A strategic group has been set
up by Russia and Ukraine to prepare joint documents on politics,
the economy, investment and military technology.
</P>
<P>
The Itar-Tass news agency reported today that the head of the
fixed member group is Sergei Yastrzhembsky, Russian President
Boris Yeltsin's press secretary and deputy director of the
President's office.
</P>
<P>
